originalText.text: Good, fast and reliable service! Printed and used the ICON online discount parking coupon that cost $30 for 6 hours of parking on Saturday evening. Recommend this garage to park your car.

originalText.text: We arrived and asked how much it would be to park and leave by Saturday morning at 10:00 am. We asked this clear as day, several times, and confirmed several times. Jose told us very plainly that to leave at that time on Saturday would be $82. When we arrived at that time on Saturday, he told us the price was now $164, and that we had misunderstood him. We hadn't. We asked to speak to his boss and insisted that he was the boss, that we had misunderstood, and that we had to pay $164. Just be aware this place will mislead you and ream you if it gets a chance.
